'''法老黃金遊行'''（{{lang-arz|موكب المومياوات الملكية}}；{{lang-en|Pharaohs' Golden Parade}}），又稱'''法老金色遊行'''，於2021年4月3日在[[埃及|埃及]][[开罗|开罗]]舉辦，將18名[[法老|法老]]與4名王后，共22具[[古埃及|古埃及]][[木乃伊|木乃伊]]從[[埃及博物館|埃及博物館]]運送到[[福斯塔特|福斯塔特]][[埃及文明國家博物館|埃及文明國家博物館]]保存。<ref>{{cite web |title=Pharaohs’ Golden Parade |url=https://egymonuments.gov.eg/en/events/pharaohs-golden-parade |website=埃及旅遊及文物部 |accessdate=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411030509/https://egymonuments.gov.eg/en/events/pharaohs-golden-parade |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=“法老的黄金游行” 22具古埃及法老木乃伊“搬家” |url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/42a0JoaXw0M |agency=环球网 |date=2021-04-04 |accessdate=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404010712/https://world.huanqiu.com/article/42a0JoaXw0M |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=埃及举行“法老的黄金游行” 22具古埃及王室木乃伊迁址 |url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-04-04/doc-ikmyaawa6162182.shtml |agency=新浪网 |date=2021-04-04 |accessdate=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210801133421/https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-04-04/doc-ikmyaawa6162182.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=埃及隆重举办盛大“法老金色游行” |url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-04-04/doc-ikmxzfmk3152458.shtml |agency=新浪网 |date=2021-04-04 |accessdate=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404010701/https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-04-04/doc-ikmxzfmk3152458.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=埃及法老黃金遊行 22具皇家木乃伊搬新家[影] |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202104040055.aspx |agency=中央社 |date=2021-04-07 |accessdate=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413030835/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202104040055.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 背景 ==
運送的22具木乃伊分別於1881年與1898年在[[代尔埃尔巴哈里|代尔埃尔巴哈里]][[DB320|皇家木乃伊坑]]與[[KV35|阿門霍特普二世墓]]發現。這些木乃伊發現以來已多次移動，直至後來安置於[[解放广场|解放广场]]埃及博物館。由於多年來考古發現不斷增多，埃及博物館逐漸無法充分展示文物，於是政府計畫修建新館，包括[[大埃及博物馆|大埃及博物馆]]與埃及文明國家博物館。舉辦遊行之前，政府開始翻新解放廣場，將[[拉美西斯二世|拉美西斯二世]]建造的[[塔尼斯|塔尼斯]][[方尖碑|方尖碑]]殘骸拼合後置於廣場中央，周圍除照明設施外由四隻[[樂蜀|樂蜀]][[卡纳克神庙|卡纳克神庙]][[斯芬克斯|斯芬克斯]]環繞。<ref>{{cite web|title=Photos: Tahrir Square lights up in final stage of development project|url=https://egyptindependent.com/photos-tahrir-square-lights-up-in-final-stage-of-development-project/|website=Egypt Independant|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410060433/https://egyptindependent.com/photos-tahrir-square-lights-up-in-final-stage-of-development-project/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 過程 ==
[[File:Royal_mummies_moved_to_Cairo_museum_in_'Golden_Parade'_-_News_360_Tv.webm|thumb]]
木乃伊裝於充[[氮氣|氮]]容器，載於埃及喪葬船裝飾的車輛運送。<ref name=Yetikyel>{{cite web |url=https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/why-egypt-paraded-22-ancient-pharaohs-through-streets-cairo-180977430/ |title=Why Egypt Paraded 22 Ancient Pharaohs Through the Streets of Cairo |last=Yetikyel |first=Gia |date=2021-04-06 |website=smithsonianmag.com |publisher=Smithsonian Institution |access-date=2021-04-19 |archive-date=2021-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428173536/https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/why-egypt-paraded-22-ancient-pharaohs-through-streets-cairo-180977430/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

遊行於當地時間午後6:30開始。有埃及藝術大師{{link-ar|纳迪尔·阿巴西|نادر_عباسي}}領銜、埃及藝術家{{link-ar|希沙姆·纳齐赫|هشام_نزيه}}作曲、穆罕默德·阿提亚指導美術<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thenationalnews.com/mena/egypt/egyptian-production-designer-mohamed-attia-says-mummies-parade-a-career-highlight-1.1209139|title=Egyptian production designer Mohamed Attia says mummies parade a career highlight|author=Nada El Sawy|publisher=[[國家報_(阿聯)|The National]]|date=2021-04-23|access-date=2021-12-18|archive-date=2021-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211124112653/https://www.thenationalnews.com/mena/egypt/egyptian-production-designer-mohamed-attia-says-mummies-parade-a-career-highlight-1.1209139|dead-url=no}}</ref>、艾哈迈德·阿爾·穆尔西指導攝影的聯合愛樂樂團表演<ref>{{cite web|url=https://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/5/35/409042/Arts--Culture/Stage--Street/Egyptian-artists-honoured-at-Cairo-Opera-House-for.aspx|title=Egyptian artists honoured at Cairo Opera House for taking part in Golden Parade|date=2021-04-12|publisher=Ahram Online|access-date=2021-12-18|archive-date=2021-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211124112653/https://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/5/35/409042/Arts--Culture/Stage--Street/Egyptian-artists-honoured-at-Cairo-Opera-House-for.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括埃及女高音歌手阿米拉·萨利姆演唱的[[埃及语|埃及语]]〈[[伊西斯|伊西斯]]頌歌〉，歌詞取自樂蜀[[代尔埃尔舍勒维特|代尔埃尔舍勒维特]]城牆銘文，其他歌詞取自《[[死者之书|死者之书]]》與[[金字塔|金字塔]]銘文。<ref>{{cite web|title=Egypt’s Soprano Amira Selim dazzles the world with exceptional performance in Pharaohs’ Golden Parade|url=https://www.egypttoday.com/Article/4/100490/Egypt%E2%80%99s-Soprano-Amira-Selim-dazzles-the-world-with-exceptional-performance|website=Egypt Today|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210408124822/https://www.egypttoday.com/Article/4/100490/Egypt%E2%80%99s-Soprano-Amira-Selim-dazzles-the-world-with-exceptional-performance|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=All you need to know about “Pharaohs Golden Parade” breathtaking symphony (Video)|url=https://see.news/pharaohs-golden-parade-symphony/|website=Sada El Balad|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410060508/https://see.news/pharaohs-golden-parade-symphony/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

遊行期間播放了多張錄影帶，包括各埃及演員在古埃及遺蹟的影像<ref>{{cite web|title=Egyptian celebrities steal mummies show in Cairo|url=https://www.arabnews.com/node/1837606/lifestyle|website=Arab News|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411061626/https://www.arabnews.com/node/1837606/lifestyle|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及埃及演員[[哈立德·埃尔-奈巴维|哈立德·埃尔-奈巴维]]近幾年國內巡迴演出的影像<ref>{{cite web|title=Video: Khaled el-Nabawy showcases recent developments of archaeologist sites in Egypt|url=https://www.egypttoday.com/Article/4/100485/Video-Khaled-el-Nabawy-showcases-recent-developments-of-archaeologist-sites|website=Egypt Today|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410060728/https://www.egypttoday.com/Article/4/100485/Video-Khaled-el-Nabawy-showcases-recent-developments-of-archaeologist-sites|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遊行期間，通往兩博物館及週邊的道路封閉，安保加強。埃及文明國家博物館門口，[[埃及總統列表|埃及總統]][[阿卜杜勒-法塔赫·塞西|阿卜杜勒-法塔赫·塞西]]接待木乃伊護送隊伍，[[共和國衛隊_(埃及)|共和國衛隊]]向車隊隊伍，並鳴了21[[敬礼#礼炮|砲]]。

總統在[[Twitter|Twitter]]發文表示：「這種雄偉景象證明埃及人民的偉大，他們是這延伸至歷史深處獨特文明的守護者。」<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-04-04|title=Egypt's Pharaohs' Golden Parade: A majestic journey that history will forever record|url=https://www.egypttoday.com/Article/4/100469/Egypt’s-Pharaohs-Golden-Parade-A-majestic-journey-that-history-will|access-date=2021-09-05|website=Egypt Today|archive-date=2021-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119084216/https://www.egypttoday.com/Article/4/100469/Egypt%E2%80%99s-Pharaohs-Golden-Parade-A-majestic-journey-that-history-will|dead-url=no}}</ref>

