try of Communications and Information Technology|url=https://mcit.gov.eg/en/Media_Center/Press_Room/Press_Releases/63281|access-date=2021-09-24|website=mcit.gov.eg|archive-date=2021-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211218162654/https://mcit.gov.eg/en/Media_Center/Press_Room/Press_Releases/63281|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-04-03|title=Photos: Egypt issues a set of postage stamps to commemorate the royal mummies parade|url=https://www.egyptindependent.com/photos-egypt-issues-a-set-of-postage-stamps-to-commemorate-the-royal-mummies-parade/|access-date=2021-09-24|website=Egypt Independent|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211218162649/https://www.egyptindependent.com/photos-egypt-issues-a-set-of-postage-stamps-to-commemorate-the-royal-mummies-parade/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

